## [1] "bb"

Matrix ()

#  matrix: matrix()

A.matrix
##      [,1] [,2] [,3] [,4] [,5] [,6]
## [1,]    1    3    5    7    9   11
## [2,]    2    4    6    8   10   12

A.matrix[1, 3]
## [1] 5
